OL,5,Cclaimants
OL,7,FA council employee who stole nearly
OL,8,F#900,000 from the accounts of
OL,9,Fvulnerable benefit claimants to fund a
OL,10,Fluxury lifestyle has been jailed for
OL,11,Ffour years and eight months.
OL,13,FRichard Shaw, 46, transferred the cash
OL,14,Fto his own bank accounts while he
OL,15,Fworked for Bolton Council's financial
OL,16,Fprotection team between 2015 and 2023.
