OL,5,Cclaimants
OL,7,FHis work role was to manage state
OL,8,Fbenefits on behalf of service users
OL,9,Fwho were unable to manage their own
OL,10,Ffinances and had no-one else to assist
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FHowever, investigations in 2023 showed
OL,14,Fseveral bank transfers totalling
OL,15,F#893,296 to nine personal accounts
OL,16,Fheld in his name, Bolton Crown Court
OL,17,Fheard.
