OL,7,FTwo BMW cars worth nearly #120,000 and
OL,8,Fseveral high-value items including
OL,9,Fcomputers and bikes were seized during
OL,10,Fa warrant at Shaw's home in Harrier
OL,11,FClose, Bolton, when he was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of fraud by abuse of
OL,13,Fposition and money laundering.
OL,15,FDuring the investigation, it was
OL,16,Festablished he spent #100,000 buying a
OL,17,Fholiday lodge in Ribble Valley,
OL,18,FLancashire, and almost #18,000 on
OL,19,Fgarden improvements.
