OL,7,FMore than #53,000 in payments to
OL,8,Fdifferent women with references such
OL,9,Fas "treat", "allowance" "nice" and
OL,10,F"ass" ` which amounted to hundreds of
OL,11,Fpounds every week ` were also made,
OL,12,Fthe court heard.
OL,14,FHe was sacked for gross misconduct in
OL,15,FMarch 2023 when the council identified
OL,16,Fand reported the possible fraud to
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police.
OL,19,FShaw pleaded guilty at an earlier
OL,20,Fhearing to one count of fraud by abuse
OL,21,Fof position.
