OL,7,FFollowing sentencing, CPS specialist
OL,8,Fprosecutor Stephanie Pendered said:
OL,9,F"Richard Shaw was entrusted with
OL,10,Fsafeguarding the finances of some of
OL,11,Fthe most vulnerable people in his
OL,12,Fcommunity. Instead, he systematically
OL,13,Fstole from them over an eight-year
OL,14,Fperiod.
