OL,4,Cstealing #900,000 from benefits
OL,5,Cclaimants
OL,7,F"His victims were people who relied on
OL,8,Fthe council because they could not
OL,9,Fmanage their own affairs. Shaw
OL,10,Fcallously exploited that
OL,11,Fvulnerability, even targeting the
OL,12,Faccounts of deceased service users
OL,13,Fknowing they would be less likely to
OL,14,Fbe checked."
OL,16,FDet Sgt Daniel Sanchez, from Greater
OL,17,FManchester Police's economic and cyber
OL,18,Fcrime unit, said: "In his role as an
OL,19,Fappointee officer, Shaw was
OL,20,Fresponsible for managing 120 client
OL,21,Fcases.
