OL,5,Cclaimants
OL,7,F"Shaw abused his position of trust
OL,8,Fwithin the council by transferring
OL,9,Fclients' money to accounts he had set
OL,10,Fup in his own name.
OL,12,F"His systematic theft and haphazard
OL,13,Fspending was uncovered by our
OL,14,Ffinancial investigator.
OL,16,F"There will now be a proceeds of crime
OL,17,Fhearing to reclaim the rest of the
OL,18,Fmoney so the council can be
OL,19,Freimbursed."
