OL,10,Fand deter corruption and this crime
OL,11,Fwas first uncovered via our own
OL,12,Finternal safeguards.
OL,14,F"We have worked closely with Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police to build the case
OL,16,Fthat has resulted in this sentence
OL,17,Fwhich reflects the gravity and impact
OL,18,Fof the crime committed.
